FW A Hallmark ECard from Lisa Kinseythought you might enjoy thisit does have sound Original Message From ENRON mailtoIMCEANOTESlisaEkinseyenronEcom NRONcom Sent Thursday April AM To Stevens Kelli Subject A Hallmark ECard from Lisa Kinsey Greetings We wanted to let you know that Lisa Kinsey created a Hallmarkcom ecard for you Click this link to see it or copy and paste this link into your Web browsers address line hmkWebsitegreetingjspidEG You can also go through our home page to see it Heres a link Once there click the ecards link then scroll to the bottom of the page to find pick up a greeting Click that link and it will ask for your email address and retrieval number Your retrieval number is EG This ecard will be available for days If youd like to send one back use the send your own greeting button beside the ecard Enjoy Jan Scott Hallmarkcom PS To us your privacy is a priority Heres a direct link to our online Privacy and Security statement if youd like to review it hmkWebsitegotojspCONTENTKEYFOOTERPRIVLEGLCONTE NTTYPEARTICLE
